{"id":1271124254,"question_id":13,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 weeks, 6 days","timestamp":1716964106,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1271124254/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"44.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int res = 0;\n        \n        \n        for(int i=0; i<s.length();i++){\n            char ch = s.charAt(i);\n            \n            switch(ch){\n                case 'I':{\n                    res++;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'V':{\n                    res+=5;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'I')\n                        res-=2;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'X':{\n                    res+=10;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'I')\n                        res-=2;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'L':{\n                    res+=50;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'X')\n                        res-=20;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'C':{\n                    res+=100;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'X')\n                        res-=20;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'D':{\n                    res+=500;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'C')\n                        res-=200;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'M':{\n                    res+=1000;\n                    if(i>0 && s.charAt(i-1) == 'C')\n                        res-=200;\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return res;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
